Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a 9 x 9 x 2 inch baking tray with cooking spray. Toss tomatoes with 1 Tbsp. of Mrs. Dash(R) Tomato Basil Garlic Blend. Lightly flatten each breast to 1/4 inch thickness. Place tomatoes and four quarters of mozzarella ball on each chicken breast. Roll up and secure with a toothpick. Place breasts on baking tray. Drizzle with the olive oil, vinegar and remaining 1 Tbsp. of Mrs. Dash(R) Tomato Basil Garlic Blend. Bake for about 30 minutes. Remove from oven, cover lightly with foil and let rest for 10 minutes.